{% block subject '[GRIIDC] DIF Submitted' %}

{% block body_html %}
Dear {{ recipient.firstName }} {{ recipient.lastName }},<br>
<br>
A Dataset Information Form (DIF) has been submitted to GRIIDC by {{ user.firstName }} {{ user.lastName }} for dataset {{ dif.dataset.udi }}. {{ user.firstName }} {{ user.lastName }} is a member of
{{ user.getResearchGroupNames() | join(', ') }} and the DIF submitted is associated with {{ dif.researchGroup.name }}.<br>
<br>
Thank you,<br>
<br>
The GRIIDC Team<br>
<br>
You are receiving this email because you are identified as a data manager for this research group. If you believe you should not be receiving this email please contact <a
href="mailto:help@griidc.org">help@griidc.org</a> for assistance.
{% endblock %}

